{"_id":"hPanic01horror","name":"H! Panic Table","type":"RollTable","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","description":"Sleepy Hollow panic table. Roll D6 + Stress Level.","formula":"1d6","results":[{"_id":"r01","type":"text","text":"1-6: Keeping it Together. You manage to keep your nerves in check. Barely.","range":[1,6],"weight":6},{"_id":"r02","type":"text","text":"7: Nervous Twitch. You and all PCs in Short range gain a stress point.","range":[7,7],"weight":1},{"_id":"r03","type":"text","text":"8: Tremble. You tremble uncontrollably. All skill rolls using Agility suffer a −2 modifier.","range":[8,8],"weight":1},{"_id":"r04","type":"text","text":"9: Drop Item. You drop a weapon or other important item—the GM decides which one.","range":[9,9],"weight":1},{"_id":"r05","type":"text","text":"10: Freeze. You're frozen by fear or stress for one round, losing your next turn.","range":[10,10],"weight":1},{"_id":"r06","type":"text","text":"11: Seek Cover. You must use your next action to move away from danger. You lose one stress point, but all other PCs in Short range gain one.","range":[11,11],"weight":1},{"_id":"r07","type":"text","text":"12: Scream. You scream for one round, losing your next turn. You lose one stress point, but every PC who hears your scream must make an immediate panic roll.","range":[12,12],"weight":1},{"_id":"r08","type":"text","text":"13: Flee. You must flee to a safe place. You lose one stress point, but every PC who hears your scream must make an immediate panic roll.","range":[13,13],"weight":1},{"_id":"r09","type":"text","text":"14: Berserk. You must immediately attack the nearest person or creature. Every PC who witnesses must make an immediate panic roll.","range":[14,14],"weight":1},{"_id":"r10","type":"text","text":"15+: Catatonic. You collapse to the floor, staring blankly into oblivion.","range":[15,20],"weight":6}],"flags":{}}
